videos.description: Alanzo Frink initially tries to pass it off but winds up taking it himself to the hoop for a big slam vs. Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Frink throws it down early for South Carolina) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Frink throws it down early for South Carolina

videos.description: Anthony Edwards fires a beautiful bounce pass in transition to Rayshaun Hammonds who quickly rises up for a slam while being fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hammonds rocks the rim for an and-1 Georgia dunk) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Hammonds rocks the rim for an and-1 Georgia dunk

videos.description: Anthony Edwards gets in the passing lane and pokes the ball away from South Carolina, then takes it downcourt for a Georgia jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards makes the steal and slam look easy) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Edwards makes the steal and slam look easy

videos.description: Keyshawn Bryant flies to the rim and jams all over his Georgia defender to pump up the crowd in South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bryant's rim-rocking slam gets Gamecock fans on their feet) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Bryant's rim-rocking slam gets Gamecock fans on their feet

videos.description: Keyshawn Bryant rushes in from the corner, picks up a pass from T.J. Moss and soars to the rim for another big slam vs. Georgia in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bryant reaches back for his second monster slam) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Bryant reaches back for his second monster slam

videos.description: Rayshaun Hammonds first pushes his way through the Gamecocks' defense for a jumper and then out of the timeout, A.J. Lawson drains a 3-pointer for South Carolina to tie the game at 77-77.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Georgia and South Carolina trade clutch plays to force OT) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Georgia and South Carolina trade clutch plays to force OT

videos.description: Keyshawn Bryant is there to clean up Jermaine Couisnard's miss in the final minute of overtime to put South Carolina ahead vs. Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bryant's and-1 putback puts South Carolina up for good in OT) 2020/2/26

videos.headline: Bryant's and-1 putback puts South Carolina up for good in OT
